meanings: Noun (가정집·호텔의) 하녀[가정부] (→barmaid, chambermaid, dairymaid, housemaid, milkmaid, nursemaid)
Noun (특정 회사에서 만든 기계장비 등의) 제품, …제
COMB in ADJ -made combines with words such as `factory' to make adjectives that indicate that something has been made or produced in a particular place or in a particular way.
